.3 \nfadein\nlinear 0.5 alpha+1.0\n\nfadeout\nlinear 0.5 alpha-1.0\n\nshake\nease 0.05 xcenter+0.02\nease 0.05 xcenter-0.02\nease 0.05 xcenter+0.02\nease 0.05 xcenter-0.02\n\nshake2\nease 0.05 xcenter+0.005\nease 0.05 xcenter-0.005\n//左右颤抖\nbounce\nease 0.15 ycenter-0.08\nease 0.15 ycenter+0.08\n\nukeru\nease 0.15 ycenter-0.01\nease 0.15 ycenter+0\n\nfururu\nease 0.07 ycenter-0.01\nease 0.1 ycenter-0\n\nsky_anime\nscale+0.5\nycenter+0.1\nease 3.0 ycenter-0.1\n//天空运镜\n\ncgchan\nscale+0.5\nxcenter-0.02\nycenter+0.2\nease 5.0 xcenter+0.05\nease 5.0 scale-0 ycenter-0 xcenter+0\ncg1_4\nscale+0.5\nease 2.0 scale-0\ncg1_1\nscale+1.5\nycenter-0.7\nease 1.0 ycenter-0.7\nease 2.0 scale-0 ycenter-0\nattack_syozen\nxcenter-0\nease 0.5 xcenter+0.25\nease 0.5 xcenter-0",
